'''乔·科斯塔''' (1992年7月17日 - )是[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[阿德莱德|阿德莱德]]一名足球运动员。他在场上司职[[中场|中场]]，现效力于[[阿德莱德联队|阿德莱德联队]] 
==俱乐部生涯==
2009年6月2日，他被阿德莱德联签下。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.adelaideunited.com.au/default.aspx?s=aleague_newsdisplay&id=27635 |title=Reds sign local talent with focus on the future |accessdate=2010-06-29 |archive-date=2011-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110404025607/http://www.adelaideunited.com.au/default.aspx?s=aleague_newsdisplay&id=27635 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

同年8月7日，他在阿德莱德联对战{{ALeague PG}}的揭幕战中，于第59分钟首次亮相。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.adelaideunited.com.au/default.aspx?s=newsdisplay&id=28608 |title=Dodd goal proves too good for Glory in season opener |accessdate=2010-06-29 |archive-date=2011-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110412203015/http://www.adelaideunited.com.au/default.aspx?s=newsdisplay&id=28608 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sportal.com.au/football-news-display/reid-injury-not-serious-75510 |title=Reid injury not serious |accessdate=2010-06-29 |archive-date=2009-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090810013308/http://sportal.com.au/football-news-display/reid-injury-not-serious-75510 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

